txt.en: 'Where is it that you come from?'
Register your heritage with the notary.

'Ah... Mirkwood.\n\n'You must be a Wood-elf of Mirkwood, once called Greenwood the Great, where King Thranduil keeps watch against the growing darkness of Dol Guldur, former stronghold of Sauron in his guise as the Necromancer.'
